Package com.cafean.client.anim

Interface RepresentitiveBean

  • All Superinterfaces:
    javax.swing.undo.StateEditable
    public interface RepresentitiveBean
extends javax.swing.undo.StateEditable
    An interface describing a bean that can update it's representation to match that of any instance of the DrawnComponent type that created it.
